# Operating System Selection and Installation

## OS Options Considered
- UGOS Pro
- TrueNAS
- Proxmox
- Other hypervisors

## Selected OS: UGOS Pro
### Rationale
- Integrated NAS features
- Native Docker and VM support
- Reduced operational complexity
- Vendor support and hardware compatibility

### Trade-offs
- Less low-level control compared to TrueNAS
- Vendor lock-in considerations
